title: Chocolate Chip Muffins with Banana
ingredients: ['340g mashed bananas', '150ml sunflower oil', '1 egg, beaten', '1 1/2 teaspoons vanilla extract', '250g plain flour', '100g caster sugar', '2 tablespoons unsweetened cocoa powder', '1 tablespoon baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '170g dark chocolate chips']
